  <p><anchor n="T.50.2062.0919c05"/><lb ed="T" n="0919c05"/><persName key="A002076">釋道元</persName>號<persName key="A002076">徹菴</persName>。<placeName key="PL000000035413">綿州</placeName>鄧氏子也。幼於<placeName key="PL000000055033">降寂<lb ed="T" n="0919c06"/>寺</placeName>出家受具。謁<persName key="A008412">大別道</persName>公。令看廓然無聖<lb ed="T" n="0919c07"/>之語。忽爾失笑曰。<persName key="A001361">達磨</persName>元來在這裏。<persName key="A008412">道公</persName>命<lb ed="T" n="0919c08"/>參<persName key="A014620">佛鑑</persName><persName key="A008397">佛眼</persName>皆蒙賞識。又投<placeName key="PL000000011011">金山</placeName>見<persName key="A001411">圓悟</persName><lb ed="T" n="0919c09"/>呈所見處。<persName key="A002076">悟</persName>弗許。值<persName key="A001411">悟</persName>被詔居<placeName key="PL000000018914">雲居</placeName>。<persName key="A002076">元</persName>從<lb ed="T" n="0919c10"/><persName key="A001411">之</persName>。雖有所入。終以鯁胸之物未散。因<persName key="A001411">悟</persName><lb ed="T" n="0919c11"/>問僧。生死到來時如何。僧曰。香臺子笑和<lb ed="T" n="0919c12"/>尚。次問及<persName key="A002076">元</persName>。<persName key="A002076">汝</persName>作麼生。<persName key="A002076">元</persName>曰。草賊大敗。<persName key="A001411">悟</persName><lb ed="T" n="0919c13"/>曰。有人問<persName key="A002076">汝</persName>時如何。<persName key="A002076">元</persName>擬答。<persName key="A001411">悟</persName>憑陵曰。草<lb ed="T" n="0919c14"/>賊大敗。<persName key="A002076">元</persName>大徹。<persName key="A001411">悟</persName>以拳擊之。<persName key="A002076">元</persName>拊掌大笑。<lb ed="T" n="0919c15"/><persName key="A001411">悟</persName>曰。<persName key="A002076">汝</persName>見甚麼便如此。曰毒拳未報永劫<lb ed="T" n="0919c16"/>不忘。</p>
